Dana Air has launched a valentine promo titled: ‘Vibe for Love’ to reward customers for their short trips to local attractions from February till mid- March, 2022. Mr. Kingsley Ezenwa, the Communications Manager, Dana Air, in a statement , stated that the promo was to encourage customers to fly with their lovers and families in this month of love to strengthen their bonds at some beautiful destinations in Nigeria. “What this promo entails is for families, lovers to book at least two tickets on the same booking reference using promo code LOVE2022 on www. flydanaair.com to get a 20 per cent discount on any of our destinations for their vibe for love staycation. DG NCAA Allays Fear Over 5G Interference With Flights NCAA Grants Premium Airline, Xejet AOC “‘The booking period will be till March 9 and travel till March 15, 2022 to give our customers taking advantage of this exciting offer ample time. Customers are also advised to watchout for vibe for love challenge launching soon across all our social media platforms.’’ ‘’It’s the month of love and as a customer – centric airline, we are using this promo to encourage lovers, families to getaway to some beautiful locations, share fun and lovely memories and strengthen their bonds while still rewarding them for choosing to fly with us for their trips in this month of love.”